\begin{abstract}  
This paper investigates entanglement dynamics in PT-symmetric non-Hermitian quantum systems. We demonstrate anomalous entanglement propagation beyond conventional Lieb-Robinson bounds in dissipative quantum walks, with experimental verification using nitrogen-vacancy centers.  
\end{abstract}  

